{
  "chapter": 21,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙回到别宫，雅夫人带来秦孝文王被吕不韦药死、异人继位为庄襄王的消息。项少龙暗忖嬴政命运，忧心赵穆阴谋消磨其壮志。次日清晨苦练骑射后，前往妮夫人处，却被公子盘设伏围攻。项少龙轻松击退十余名王族少年，将公子盘带回书房教训，以恩威并施之法收服其心，教其柔道摔跤技法。妮夫人见劣子转变，对项少龙暗生好感。随后项少龙被赵王后召见，少君告状踢屁股之事。赵王后设下比武之局，项少龙以精湛搏击术轻松击倒二十名力士，赢得赵王后及众妃嫔倾慕。赵王后欲留他在后宫沐浴更衣，项少龙以出使魏国为由婉拒，众宫女趁机为他穿衣时大占便宜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孝文王今年五十三岁，一向体弱多病，但今天他却是因吃了吕不韦献上的药而致死的，所以无人不怀疑是吕不韦暗下的手脚，只是碍于庄襄王与吕不韦的关系，故敢怒不敢言。唉！吕不韦这人野心极大，手段又毒辣厉害，现在各国人人自危，怕秦军很快便有东侵的行动。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦长年行商，往来各地，对各国的情势有深入的了解，若给他当权，后果会更严重。商人只讲实利，不顾道义，不受意气驱策，这样的人进行扩张政策，想想都教人心寒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在秦国由何人当宰相？情况又是如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "何人掌权并不重要，这相国之位迟早都要落入吕不韦手中。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅姊为何这么怕秦人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "不是我怕秦人，而是没有人不怕他们。看看我们赵国便清楚，谁不沉迷在荒淫萎靡、醇酒美人的生活里，敌兵临城时便振作一下，敌人一退又故态复萌；而秦人仍保持着戎狄的刻苦耐劳，尽量不受南方的风气沾染，商鞅为秦人'焚《诗》、《书》'，正是逢迎秦人禁止诗书，国必富强的心态。奴家虽不知谁对谁错，但观乎秦人日益强大，便不能说秦人焚诗书没有理由。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "范雎拜相前，秦国大权旁落到穰侯手上，掌权的全是他派系的人，采取所谓远攻近交的策略，使秦国长年劳师远征，国力消耗；秦昭襄王于是与范雎密谋，一举夺回军权，改远攻近交为远交近攻，与齐、楚修好，全力对付韩国和我们，致有长平之战，王兄又走错了棋，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "过去的便让它过去，不要多想了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "穰侯下台后，他的敌系大将白起与范雎一向不和，白起在长平一役坑我四十万降兵，手段空前残忍，范雎以此大做文章，最后终于说服秦王把白起族诛。此事亦惹起秦国军方众将领对范雎这些外籍人的仇视，现在由燕国来的客卿蔡泽取代相位，不过吕不韦刻下水涨船高，蔡泽当好景不长了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "唉！什么都不用想，今朝有酒今朝醉，明日愁来明日当。来！我们立即入房行乐。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "两女",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "'今朝有酒今朝醉，明日愁来明日当'，项郎说得真好。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快揍他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "再哭一声，我赏你十记耳光。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人一是将他交给我，一是我以后袖手不理。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是交给先生哩！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "这就最好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "坐下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "看！你这是成什么样子，自己没有本领，却找人帮忙，想以众凌寡，输了又哭又喊，算什么英雄好汉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你才不是英雄好汉，以大欺小。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "你若怕我，就不会主动来惹我，可知这并非以大欺小的问题，而是谁强谁弱的问题。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚才你踢少君的屁股，他定会告知大王，斩你的头。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "我见你这么年纪小小，便懂得调戏女人，还以为你是个人物，哪知斗不过人，却只懂用卑鄙手段，我看错你了，滚吧！我以后都不想见到你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何我捉弄那些女人，你还当我是个人物？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "凡是男人，大都好色，年纪大小，并无分别，那天我见你轻薄那位姊姊时，颇有手段，还以为你其他的功夫都不赖，怎知如此窝囊，有志气的便学得比我更有本领，正正式式把我击倒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "终有一天我会打败你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "只是口头说说有什么用，还是滚吧！我最讨厌只懂空言的无用之徒，希望你永远不用到沙场去，否则就不是被踢屁股那么简单了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若我听你的话，你会否教我刚才打人的本领？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "你知否我的本领多么珍贵，哪会凭你娘一句话便传给你，想学嘛！还要通过考验才行。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "但若你听话，我不但可使你成为赵国真正的英雄和剑手，还可以教你成为迷死女人的爱情高手，天下美女，任你予取予携。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真的吗？我要通过什么考验？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "首先是捱揍，捱不得揍的人哪有资格打架。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "你去找其他人试试我教的技法吧！若听教听话，将来定会变得像我般高大强壮，本领过人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "假若我教小公子如何去和女人亲热，夫人会怎样想呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "小孩子最是反叛好奇，夫人你愈禁制他，他愈想打破禁制，所以不若让他清楚自己在做什么，会有什么后果，应负上什么责任，他反会节制自己。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可是他只有十三岁啊！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人嫁人时多大年纪呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那时妾身只有十四岁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以呢！十三岁不算小了，十五岁的男人有妻有妾的大有人在，兼之宫廷风气如此，夫人想阻止他不近女色，看来也难以办到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但妾身总觉得他还是个不懂事的孩子，不过先生的想法很精辟独特，妾身从未听过其他人有这种看法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妮夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
      "speaker_name": "卫士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人奉命行事，其他的都不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带兵卫项少龙拜见王后。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "text": "母后！就是他踢了我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "赵王后",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "连少君你都敢冒犯，项少龙你可知此乃死罪。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "text": "小臣现在知罪，但当时小臣并不知道围攻我的十多人里有少君在，只是奉妮夫人旨意，希望能好好管教公子盘，又为了自卫，才犯下此罪，请王后明鉴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "赵王后",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事情究竟如何？你给我清楚道来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "text": "母后定要为王儿作主。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "赵王后",
      "listener": "char_shao_jun",
      "text": "你想怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "赵王后",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我站起来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "赵王后",
      "listener": "char_shao_jun",
